<promed@promedmail.org>

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of the Philippines can be seen at http://healthmap.org/r/2BYy. Catanduanes (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catanduanes) an island province of the Philippines located in the Bicol Region in Luzon. Its capital is Virac and the province lies to the east of Camarines Sur across Maqueda Channel. - Mod.LL]

******
[3] Cholera - India (Rajasthan State)
Date: Sun 17 Jun 2012
Source: The Times of India, Times News Network (TNN) [edited]
http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-17/jaipur/32281338_1_cholera-cases-door-to-door-survey-poor-quality-drinking-water


One more case of cholera was detected in the city of Jaipur on Sat 16 Jun 2012, taking the total number of cases to 4 in the past 20 days.

3 of the cases have been confirmed by the medical, health and family welfare department, while 1 case of cholera was admitted to the LK Lon hospital, and discharged after treatment on Fri 15 Jun 2012.

